# SHX/SHP Repair Tool - Harita Hive Data Tool
# MIT License
#
# Fix broken shapefiles, regenerate missing SHX/DBF files
# Recovers corrupted spatial data with advanced repair algorithms
#
# Features:
# - Automatic detection of shapefile corruption
# - Regeneration of missing .shx index files
# - Repair of corrupted .dbf attribute tables
# - Recovery of partial geometry data
# - Projection file (.prj) reconstruction
# - Batch repair for multiple files
#
# Repair Capabilities:
# - Missing or corrupted .shx files
# - Truncated or damaged .shp files
# - Invalid geometry reconstruction
# - Attribute table recovery
# - Character encoding fixes
# - Spatial index rebuilding
#
# Recovery Methods:
# - Header information analysis
# - Geometry validation and repair
# - Attribute type inference
# - Coordinate system detection
# - Topology reconstruction
#
# Validation Features:
# - Geometry validity checking
# - Attribute consistency verification
# - Spatial reference validation
# - File integrity assessment
# - Recovery success reporting
#
# Usage:
# shx-shp-repair --input broken_shapefile.shp --output repaired_shapefile.shp
# shx-shp-repair --batch-repair corrupted_files/ --validate-output